cast.overview: Inspired by her mom's rebellious past and a confident new friend, a shy 16-year-old publishes an anonymous zine calling out sexism at her school.
cast.title: Moxie

details.biography: Lauren Tsai (born February 11, 1998), also known as Lala (ララ), is a Chinese-American illustrator, model, and actress. She is best known to audiences for her appearance in the Fuji TV and Netflix series Terrace House: Aloha State. She made her acting debut in the third and final season of Legion, a television series based on the Marvel Comics character of the same name.
details.name: Lauren Tsai
